snippet.title: Densha De GO! Nagoya Railroad - Gifu Streetcar
snippet.description:
From the excellent Densha de Go Nagoya Railroad, released in 2000 for the Playstation. Emulated with XEBRA. This is a tricky route, especially the street running sections.

Unfortunately the real Gifu streetcar system closed in 2005
